race.comment: SMART SHAZZA (9) is a consistent conveyance who has a win and two seconds from just four spins around this circuit. Will be rock-hard fit for this and looks the one they all have to run down. ONE BEAT NO BEAT (6) has been plying his trade in harder races in town and will appreciate the drop back in company here. Top-three commodity on best form. The well-related A TOUCH FROM FAYT (12) (half to G3 winner Wapiti) is drawn to get all the favours from the inside alley and should give backers a sight. DRIALLE (2) will be at peak fitness now third-up and may make his presence felt. AIR MARSHAL (5) gets some weight off from the low draw and should be included in calculations.
